highlights.text: “Yummy” by Justin Bieber is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Alone, Pt. II” by Alan Walker and Ava Max is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 76 spots at #97.
J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #13.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 157 weeks straight.
